  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    Reuse the Workspace case implementation by extracting a shared helper (e.g., `EmitWorkspaceTabOpenAndStreamAsync`) — DRY principle. Both = Workspace + ack; FormPrefill = no-op; SideEffect = telemetry only. Each task adds a distinct case branch.
